WEBVTT

00:01.800 --> 00:04.098
Okay, a couple of things
before we get started.

00:04.130 --> 00:06.269
You are a witness appearing
before a grand jury

00:06.300 --> 00:08.131
in Cook County
and not its target.

00:08.170 --> 00:10.764
