to have an attorney with you

00:10.810 --> 00:12.675
to answer any questions
that you might have.

00:12.710 --> 00:13.802
Do you understand that?

00:13.840 --> 00:14.670
BLAKE:
Yes.

00:17.180 --> 00:18.772
Blake Calamar.

00:18.810 --> 00:23.110
That's C-A-L-A-M-A-R.

00:23.150 --> 00:24.617
Have you and I
ever met before?
Yes,

00:24.650 --> 00:27.710
uh, we have, when
you searched my apartment

00:27.760 --> 00:29.159
and threatened me.

00:29.190 --> 00:30.726
Have we kissed
and made up?

00:30.760 --> 00:32.125
Not really.

00:32.160 --> 00:33.718
Uh, but I intend to tell

00:33.760 --> 00:35.193
the truth here, anyway.

00:35.230 --> 00:36.788
