granted immunity.

00:36.830 --> 00:38.661
Well, I'd tell
the truth either way,

00:38.700 --> 00:40.292
but a little immunity
never hurt.

00:40.340 --> 00:41.796
(laughter)
Gary...

00:41.840 --> 00:43.159
where are you
going with this?

00:43.210 --> 00:44.165
I'm showing how
he has knowledge

00:44.210 --> 00:45.165
of criminal activity.

00:45.210 --> 00:46.404
They don't give a rat's ass.

00:46.440 --> 00:47.475
Get on with it.

00:47.510 --> 00:50.479
Where are you employed,
Mr. Calamar?

00:50.510 --> 00:54.412
Until recently, I was employed
at Lockhart/Gardner & Bond.

00:54.450 --> 00:56.816
And you were brought there
by Mr. Derrick Bond,

00:56.850 --> 00:58.147
is that correct?
Yes.

00:58.190 --> 00:59.657
CARY:
And he was recently forced out.

00:59.690 --> 01:02.420
BLAKE:
By the other partners,
uh, Diane Lockhart

01:02.460 --> 01:03.552
and Will Gardner.

01:03.590 --> 01:05.182
